-interests-over-the-gaza-war/0000018b-a917-d15f-a3db-bfd75d390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队展示了加沙人在撤离到加沙地带以南时挥舞白旗的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-live/pm-no-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages-jewish-man-killed-at-la-protest/0000018b-a7f5-dc0b-a1cb-e7f72f5d0000</link><description>以色列军队称没有袭击加沙的 Al-Shifa 医院，否认哈马斯的说法 ■ 以色列国防军称下午从黎巴嫩发射了 30 枚火箭弹；以色列国防军称下午从黎巴嫩发射了 30 枚火箭弹。哈马斯声称对海法地区 18 人枪击事件负责 ■ 边境警察在耶路撒冷袭击中丧生 ■ 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀中至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生，241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部: 超过10,000人被杀</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 09:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-live/pm-no-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages-jewish-man-killed-at-la-protest/0000018b-a7f5-dc0b-a1cb-e7f72f5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府改变了在战争期间冻结信息自由请求的意图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/government-backtracks-on-intention-to-freeze-freedom-of-information-requests-during-war/0000018b-a8e6-d9c0-a5fb-e9fe71f20000</link><description>在公众压力和非政府组织的努力下，政府表示信息自由请求将正常处理，尽管之前由于持续的战争而出现延误</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 09:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/government-backtracks-on-intention-to-freeze-freedom-of-information-requests-during-war/0000018b-a8e6-d9c0-a5fb-e9fe71f20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡向美国广播公司新闻表示：如果不释放以色列人质，加沙就不会停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-abc-news-no-gaza-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018b-a87b-dc41-af9f-eb7b0e760000</link><description>当被问及他是否认为自己应该为以色列因哈马斯的袭击而措手不及承担责任时，内塔尼亚胡回答说：“当然。”这不是一个问题。战争结束后就会解决”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 07:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-abc-news-no-gaza-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018b